main event: A military sighting of an object similar to a satellite on November 14.
interesting points: The object traversed 62 degrees of bearing in 8 seconds,The observation was made from the ground with a 50-degree elevation,The sighting was attributed to a very high meteor,The weather conditions were clear with 3-5 cloud coverage,No photographs or physical evidence were collected.
sighted object: object similar in appearance to a satellite
